window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The FBI is digging dangerously close to the paranormal truth. In fact, they are observing Zach like he's some mobster kingpin. </p> <p>Then again, with a new giant mansion filled with beautiful ladies and a hoard brimming with gold, is being the dragon king all that different?</p> <p>Zach is trying to button up his business and appear innocuous to the outside world, but Norton decides to play dirty. When Norton takes the gloves off and changes the rules, is he ready for what the dragon king has in store for him?</p> <p>All of this while Zach has to juggle a house full of nymphs and keep his mates satisfied....</p>"; 
